be ready to fight and sat back on his haunches, watching the Maximal 
now Pred and some stranger. hHe looked up at the arrival of his leader.

"Big bo-...," the young Maximal trailed off as the familar nickname he 
had grown acustomed to calling his former leader. He dropped his head, 
before raising it and continuing. "I'm not sure Rodimus."
